{"type": "article", "id": 2749, "title": "Bernhardt Design 125 周年纪念版椅子", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-10T08:04:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232520eHMuDz4XwBRIfNtp.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t为了纪念公司成立125 周年，美国家具设计商 Bernhardt Design 力邀英国设计师 Ross Lovegrove 带来了一款名为“ Anne ”的椅子，体现出品牌多年以来木工工艺方面的卓越传统。Ross Lovegrove 模仿典型的美国法院使用的椅子，做出来了一款木制椅子，靠背呈向后倾斜之势，四个椅角则向外撇开。他希望借助这一美国历史元素，创造出一把具有现代感的椅子，能够体现他的设计语言。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232518qPepTav1KhDrVjgB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232519ju8mSaJABnZPGw9s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232519AYpPqR4FlMhnkeBU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}